{"tid":1092932,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友話感情變淡而變成我PTBF","createTime":"2019-04-05T08:36:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-05T08:56:58.000Z","uid":102575,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"95bbe8eaff3683efc0c734c40ec00d36e503956c","tid":1092932,"uid":102575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T08:36:01.000Z","msg":"呢幾日男朋友同嘈交，初初佢話對我感情變淡，希望我知道佢冇可能好似當初咁鐘意我，又話畀我決定之後點處理段感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我聽完覺得其實佢想同我分手，於是用盡全力去了解到底我地邊一part 出現問題。<br />\n<br />\n佢堅持唔係同我分手，而係覺得我地未來人生方向唔一樣，加上平時一d所謂差異而覺得我地唔會行到落去(佢完全冇同我講過自己單方面扣我分...)<br />\n<br />\n佢仲話其實心態上由男朋友變咗我PTBF<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n約我出街係因為佢認為我想見佢，不過過程中又唔會主動同我有任何身體接觸，我主動拖手同抱佢佢仲會縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唉屌，我寧願自己出錢請個真PTBF，起碼我會得到我想要嘅skinship 先啦係咪?!?!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  明明開始嘅時候，所有身體接觸都係佢做主動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n雖然我地達成共識，其實大家仲係著緊大家，唔會分手住，不過我發覺咁落去會令自己好辛苦。就算佢以後有咩行動去氹我，我都會亂諗到底佢係出於真心定真係當自己PTBF<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢到底當我係乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5057f3efa282658e4ce44d6111c1cd3ca04639d","tid":1092932,"uid":229906,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T08:37:49.000Z","msg":"水泡"},{"pid":"70fe87db43db2391e4073aa14fb0a43a21a8c81a","tid":1092932,"uid":102575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T08:39:47.000Z","msg":"求屌醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 份人好易心軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0097346fd71fc818c7f4b56c828662a55f581f06","tid":1092932,"uid":227635,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T08:46:21.000Z","msg":"想逼你講分手，冷暴力"},{"pid":"f1725b92a7ed9beeb6a7820437793b6d67a4d7a9","tid":1092932,"uid":102190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T08:50:55.000Z","msg":"可能你變柒咗<br />\n或者當初佢係唔睇樣個種人，但依家係"},{"pid":"2a8e6fefdcdcb25a51ab9c0c6010dec42e8cdb81","tid":1092932,"uid":102575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1725b92a7ed9beeb6a7820437793b6d67a4d7a9","tid":1092932,"uid":102190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T08:50:55.000Z","msg":"可能你變柒咗<br />\n或者當初佢係唔睇樣個種人，但依家係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T08:52:47.000Z","msg":"一齊咗之後我反而打扮多咗，會化妝會扮靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebaad8cabc035bd7445f9d526bc835a3ed8729ba","tid":1092932,"uid":241459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T08:55:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"952af43765c5b28be08000d0f1b9c6b1eaa3e035","tid":1092932,"uid":187162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T08:56:58.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪Ipaid？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}